# RÃ©cupÃ©rer la sÃ©lection
if result:
    selected_image = result["selected_image"]
    selected_url = result["selected_url"]
    current_index = result["current_index"]
```

## ğŸ¨ Personnalisation

### ParamÃ¨tres disponibles

```python
